About this item

  • The New M5 Band Comes With A 0.96inch HD Screen and Sleek Light Weight Yet Durable Design Which Makes It Very Comfortable To Wear And Carry Around.
  • It is compatible with devices having Bluetooth version 4.0 and below in smartphones, tablets, and PC's and also supports Android and IOS Working: To connect the smart band to the mobile phone, you need to connect the current mobile successfully via Bluetooth.
  • Magnetic charging – Hassle free charging PAI (Personal Activity Intelligence) – Single matrix to track your all fitness related activities.; Waterproof: Not for swimming or diving Standby time: 15days & above this product uses professional Bluetooth RF signal and custom algorithm.
  • Activity Tracker Mode – M5 band has many modes for recording your workout sessions. You can track the number of steps you took during your workout and the distance traveled in KM while running or walking
  • Human Interface Input: Touch Screen; Included Components: Pfm5 Smart Band, Charging Cable, User Manual; Compatible Devices: Tabletsmartphone; Connectivity Technology: Usb

Product description

MELBON M5 Smartwatch Fitness Band is one unique product which is Unique, Affordable and Light weight, weighing only 25 gm and yet so Powerful for quite a lot of Purposes. You can Just Charge it Full as Quick as in 2 Hrs, and Go on for Long, Just Do a Lot of Purposeful Stuff attaching it to a Bluetooth Phone, check Blood Pressure, Heart Rate with the Monitor, shows your Steps Walked, Messaging Apps Notifications, equipped with a Sleep Monitor for better health Checks and the Battery is Just too Good, 150 mAh which lasts as long as 8 days, 192 hrs. The Wide Range, Superior Quality Manufacturing and Feature List which Just Doesn't end is a Boon for Each and Every Customer.
